sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { HCardViewSection, HCardViewContainer, HCardViewTitle, HCard, HCardHead, HCardTitle, HCardAvatarContainer, HCardContent, HCardContentContainer, HCardContentItem, AvatarImage, } from "./styled"; export const HCardView = () => { const handleOnChange = () => {}; let givenName, surname, email, phone, houseNumberOrName, street, suburb, state, postcode, country; return ( hCard Preview {givenName || "-"} {surname || "-"} Email {email} Phone {phone} Address {houseNumberOrName} {street} {`${suburb}${suburb && state && ","} ${state}`} Postcode {postcode} Country {country} ); };
